{"tid":2189702,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"Palantir討論區","createTime":"2020-09-05T05:36:38.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-07T06:04:06.000Z","uid":365423,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":25,"replies":[{"pid":"4c474e8adce6bf7f9c75398db4850ea93658e406","tid":2189702,"uid":365423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-09-05T05:36:38.000Z","msg":"仲未上市就燈定先<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"gold\"><span class=\"small\">Aug. 25, 2020 9:54 pm</span></span><br />\n<br />\nPalantir Technologies Inc. has a message for investors awaiting the tech company&rsquo;s long-anticipated stock listing: It has soured on Silicon Valley.<br />\n<br />\nThe money-losing, data-focused software company, which was once one of the world&rsquo;s most valuable startups, launched a broadside against the tech sector as it unveiled paperwork Tuesday to take itself public through a direct listing slated for later this year&mdash;one that could come as soon as next month.<br />\n<br />\nChief Executive Alex Karp, who co-founded the company along with the billionaire investor Peter Thiel and others, spent much of an introductory letter lambasting the business models of other software companies and criticizing the tech giants of Silicon Valley for being out of touch with American principles and societal needs.<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"blue\"><span class=\"gold\">Palantir S1文件</span></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1321655/000119312520230013/d904406ds1.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.sec.gov%2FArchives%2Fedgar%2Fdata%2F1321655%2F000119312520230013%2Fd904406ds1.htm&d=RlZLtXxvTyjhSejQ4AJs41m6lgSi2KDQroqMKj6vOm8%3D&h=636ce306\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.sec.gov/Archives/edgar/data/1321655/000119312520230013/d904406ds1.htm</a>"},{"pid":"6ce9051c0a6f99d28917baaaaa3b18b1cd8950fd","tid":2189702,"uid":365423,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"4c474e8adc